<p><span class="anchor" id="p70"></span>وَلَو قَالَ إِن كَانَ بِبَطْنِهَا ذكر<a href="#p70" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p71"></span>فَلهُ كَذَا<a href="#p71" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
